    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El walks down the same street with Albie and MADISON, and now a third dog, TOZER. Albie and MADISON are leashed in one of El‚Äôs hands, TOZER in the other.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Transition">
      <Text>QUICK CUT TO:</Text>
