    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El walks down the same street, with Albie, MADISON, and TOZER, but now with addition of GABRIEL MAGNUS, PRINCESS VICTORIA, and BOO. El is being pulled along by the sheer force of the dogs, a force that she embraces and doesn‚Äôt mind being pulled by.</Text>
