      <Text>Ext. apartment complex / courtyard - afternoon</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>CAMERA sees just over JEANNIE‚Äôs shoulder, tracking her wandering and meandering pace. In the same frame‚Äôs FOREGROUND, we can see the blur of El and Albie come into focus. At first, El and Albie darts towards JEANNIE. But just short of reaching her, El slows down to a normal pace.</Text>
