      <Text>Cut to:</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>ext. jeannie‚Äôs apartment - afternoon</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>CAMERA sees a stretch of courtyard from their flank, El and Albie enter the frame from the left hand side, JEANNIE, enters the frame from the right hand side‚Äîthey‚Äôre walking dead on towards each other. Stopping directly in front of JEANNIE‚Äôs front door.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El sends Albie over to get JEANNIE‚Äôs attention. Albie approaches JEANNIE, and once the dog enters her periphery, she shrieks.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Jeannie</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Oh god, control your dog for christ‚Äôs sakes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>JEANNIE looks up from her phone and realizes it is El.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>JEANNIE (CONT'D)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Oh, hi, El. You snuck right up on me. How are you, sweetie?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El gestures ‚Äòso so.‚Äô</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Jeannie (CONT'D)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>How‚Äôd you end up with her mutt?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El doesn‚Äôt respond.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Jeannie (CONT'D)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Well, nice catching up with you. Tell your mother I said ‚Äúhello.‚Äù</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>JEANNIE makes to circumnavigate the El and Albie blockage. JEANNIE moves around them and makes her way to her front door.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El reaches into a pocket, pulls out a laminated questionnaire, taps on JEANNIE‚Äôs shoulder, and hands her the card.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Cut to:</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>int. Jeannie‚Äôs apartment / kitchen - afternoon</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El, JEANNIE, and WALTER sit around their kitchen table. WALTER is JEANNIE‚Äôs second husband, and he is also much younger than JEANNIE.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="22 3/8" Page="64" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>CLOSE ON WALTER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Flash Cut to:</Text>
