    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>TEDDY, SUE, NICOLE, OMAR, MICAH, and El sit on a Frankenstein couch set in a circle around a coffee table, each of them with their laptops open on their laps.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Each one of them cycles through a pdf of the cropped out faces from Sheen‚Äôs polaroids.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Nicole</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Ugh. This one here‚Äî</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>CLOSE on GARY‚Äôs CROPPED FACE.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Nicole (cont‚Äôd)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Total fucking creep. I moved in before Fall semester my freshman year. I still wasn‚Äôt 18 until December. So I‚Äôm moving my shit in, and Gary comes out of nowhere and offers to help out, not without first staring me up and down. After some weird flirty comments, I tell him I‚Äôm 17, he puts his hand on my lower back, he whispers into my ear, ‚ÄúAnd?‚Äù</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
