    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Sue</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>And your old ass balls should be lucky to have a seat next to a pair of old ass tits.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Nicole</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Pigs.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Teddy</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Oink. Oink.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Omar</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Bacon?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Micah</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>We ain‚Äôt the police.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Omar</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Yo, Susan, what about this guy? He‚Äôs been in here before.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Sue</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>What page?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Teddy</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Seventeen.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Sue</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Yeah, Sal. He delivers us our medicine. He‚Äôs also in a few of these pictures you sent us.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>FLASH on CLOSE UPS of MULTIPLE SHOTS of SAL‚Äôs FACE.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El types into the group chat they have set up: ‚Äúmedicine? Do you mean drugs?‚Äù</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Micah</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>What‚Äôs the difference?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Teddy</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>One has lobbyists.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Nicole</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Okay, Karl Marx.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Sue</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>(to El)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>He sells us weed. He‚Äôs cheap, he comes to us. Pretty good deal.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El types into the group chat: ‚Äúdoes he come here a lot?‚Äù</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Sue</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>We only call him whenever we run out. Forgot that he knew Sheen.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Micah</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>You know when he‚Äôs a fucking mile away his car is so loud. He‚Äôs here all the goddamned time.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El types into the group chat: ‚Äúwhat does he drive?‚Äù</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Micah</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Yellow corvette with a modified exhaust.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Omar</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>So fucking annoying.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Teddy</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>It‚Äôs so fucking sexy.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El types into the group chat: ‚Äúdoes he sell other things?‚Äù</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
