      <Text>I asked him for Adderal once, and he obliged.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Micah</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Those weren‚Äôt Adderal, bro. We crushed those bitches up and sniffed them and that shit was Ritalin.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Teddy</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Yeah, remember Omar got super racist. We were all smokin cigs and these black kids were just down the way. Micah was dying to try and fight them.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
