    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Some of her followers found information regarding the different drug baggie patterns El posted. They lead her in different directions: the dark web, local sex shop websites (here they sell baggies to local drug dealers masquerading as button baggies), and a few news stories.</Text>
