    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Dave</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El‚Äî</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>(he starts with exasperation, then takes a breather reconsidering his approach)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>‚ÄîWalter, he‚Äôs a shithead, but I don‚Äôt think he killed anyone, sweetie. Don‚Äôt think he can even if he tried. He‚Äôs just some money hungry young jerk trying to grab Jeannie‚Äôs 9/11 insurance cash out. As for Gary, I‚Äôve known him since he moved in. We‚Äôve both helped each other plenty and he gives me work every now and then. Believe me, El‚ÄîGary, he‚Äôs a stand up guy.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El hurries back to the table, and closes her laptop.</Text>
