    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>JULIAN walks from behind El to the forefront of El, leading her into the darkened house. JULIAN is the owner of the APARTMENT COMPLEX where El lives. He is a fit, EASTERN EUROPEAN, wearing loose boxers, his body glistens with sweat. His face is obscured up until this point.</Text>
