      <Text>You lied, little girl. I don‚Äôt like liars. But I do like your balls. Balls are something I can appreciate. You got a pair of big balls underneath those tight jeans, sweetie?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El starts to follow JULIAN, but he halts, his body looming over. The CAMERA tracks up and we can see JULIAN‚Äôs face, he has a giant scar running across the top of his scalp.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Julian</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
