    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>El continues to look around the place.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Cut to:</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>int. Mansion / Julian‚Äôs bedroom - morning</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>JULIAN changes his clothing.</Text>
