    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Int. Mansion / foyer - morning</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>When El hears the sounds of JULIAN returning she hurries back to the spot she was standing in when he left, attempting to keep up appearances.</Text>
